('金银花种子', 'SEED', jsonb_build_object('grow_time', 36, 'reharvest', 0, 'production_items', jsonb_build_array(jsonb_build_object('weight', 1, 'template_id', (SELECT id FROM xt_item_template WHERE name='金银花')))),  '["seed","herb","dual","uncommon"]', '金银花的种子，金花银蕊并蒂而生，阴阳调和的妙药。'),
('元阳草种子', 'SEED', jsonb_build_object('grow_time', 36, 'reharvest', 0, 'production_items', jsonb_build_array(jsonb_build_object('weight', 1, 'template_id', (SELECT id FROM xt_item_template WHERE name='元阳草')))),  '["seed","herb","yang","uncommon"]', '元阳草的种子，正午播种效力最盛，入药纯阳驱阴。'),
('太阴菇孢子', 'SEED', jsonb_build_object('grow_time', 40, 'reharvest', 0, 'production_items', jsonb_build_array(jsonb_build_object('weight', 1, 'template_id', (SELECT id FROM xt_item_template WHERE name='太阴菇')))),  '["seed","herb","yin","uncommon"]', '太阴菇的孢子，只在子夜洒落，阴气越重长势越好。'),
('赤炼果种子', 'SEED', jsonb_build_object('grow_time', 48, 'reharvest', 0, 'production_items', jsonb_build_array(jsonb_build_object('weight', 1, 'template_id', (SELECT id FROM xt_item_template WHERE name='赤炼果')))),  '["seed","herb","fire","uncommon"]', '赤炼果的种子，种在火脉灵田里果皮才会变得滚烫。'),
('九穗禾种子', 'SEED', jsonb_build_object('grow_time', 48, 'reharvest', 0, 'production_items', jsonb_build_array(jsonb_build_object('weight', 1, 'template_id', (SELECT id FROM xt_item_template WHERE name='九穗禾')))),  '["seed","herb","grain","uncommon"]', '一茎九穗的灵禾种子，成熟时金黄飘香，蕴含大地精华。'),
('七星草种子', 'SEED', jsonb_build_object('grow_time', 60, 'reharvest', 0, 'production_items', jsonb_build_array(jsonb_build_object('weight', 1, 'template_id', (SELECT id FROM xt_item_template WHERE name='七星草')))),  '["seed","herb","star","rare"]', '七星草的种子，夜间吸北斗七星之力，叶片银斑如星辰排列。'),
('曼陀罗种子', 'SEED', jsonb_build_object('grow_time', 72, 'reharvest', 0, 'production_items', jsonb_build_array(jsonb_build_object('weight', 1, 'template_id', (SELECT id FROM xt_item_template WHERE name='曼陀罗')))),  '["seed","herb","poison","rare"]', '曼陀罗的种子，剧毒，种植时需万分谨慎，入药更需小心。'),
('玄黄根苗', 'SEED', jsonb_build_object('grow_time', 96, 'reharvest', 0, 'production_items', jsonb_build_array(jsonb_build_object('weight', 1, 'template_id', (SELECT id FROM xt_item_template WHERE name='玄黄根')))), '["seed","herb","earth","rare"]', '玄黄根的根苗，需深埋灵土三尺，一季方成，玄皮黄心如人形。'),
('千年灵芝种子', 'SEED', jsonb_build_object('grow_time', 72, 'reharvest', 0, 'production_items', jsonb_build_array(jsonb_build_object('weight', 1, 'template_id', (SELECT id FROM xt_item_template WHERE name='千年灵芝')))), '["seed","herb","rare"]', '千年灵芝的种子，种下需等待三日方熟。通体金纹，丹师眼中可遇不可求。'),
('断肠草种子', 'SEED', jsonb_build_object('grow_time', 60, 'reharvest', 0, 'production_items', jsonb_build_array(jsonb_build_object('weight', 1, 'template_id', (SELECT id FROM xt_item_template WHERE name='断肠草')))), '["seed","herb","poison","rare"]', '断肠草的种子，闻之清甜种之剧毒，务必戴手套播种。'),
('蛇涎果种子', 'SEED', jsonb_build_object('grow_time', 36, 'reharvest', 0, 'production_items', jsonb_build_array(jsonb_build_object('weight', 1, 'template_id', (SELECT id FROM xt_item_template WHERE name='蛇涎果')))), '["seed","herb","poison","uncommon"]', '蛇涎果的种子，需用蛇妖唾液灌溉，普通修士还是别乱碰为好。'),
('忘忧草种子', 'SEED', jsonb_build_object('grow_time', 60, 'reharvest', 0, 'production_items', jsonb_build_array(jsonb_build_object('weight', 1, 'template_id', (SELECT id FROM xt_item_template WHERE name='忘忧草')))), '["seed","herb","mind","rare"]', '忘忧草的种子，淡蓝色的种子如泪滴。种出来偶尔嚼一口可以，多吃会变傻。'),
('天蚕卵', 'SEED', jsonb_build_object('grow_time', 72, 'reharvest', 0, 'production_items', jsonb_build_array(jsonb_build_object('weight', 1, 'template_id', (SELECT id FROM xt_item_template WHERE name='天蚕')))), '["seed","silk","rare"]', '天蚕的卵，孵化后吐出的丝轻如云韧如钢。养蚕修士的最爱。'),
('九天仙草种子', 'SEED', jsonb_build_object('grow_time', 168, 'reharvest', 0, 'production_items', jsonb_build_array(jsonb_build_object('weight', 1, 'template_id', (SELECT id FROM xt_item_template WHERE name='九天仙草')))), '["seed","herb","immortal","epic"]', '九天仙草的种子，传说只在天之极巅发芽。种在福地已是天大的机缘，七日浴朝霞方得。'),
('琉璃仙菇孢子', 'SEED', jsonb_build_object('grow_time', 144, 'reharvest', 0, 'production_items', jsonb_build_array(jsonb_build_object('weight', 1, 'template_id', (SELECT id FROM xt_item_template WHERE name='琉璃仙菇')))), '["seed","herb","crystalline","epic"]', '琉璃仙菇的孢子，落地时闪烁着七彩光芒。传闻只在秘境现世。');
